      "settings": {
        "code": "<div class=\"t4s-text-center\" style=\"padding: 15px 0;color: #fff;\">\n    <div class=\"footer-seo\">\n        <h2>NG EarSafe Open-Ear Bluetooth Headphones: Unleash Wireless Freedom with Unmatched Comfort</h2>\n        \n        <h3>Innovative Open-Ear Technology</h3>\n        <p>\n            Crafted for those who crave both situational awareness and exceptional audio fidelity, the NG EarSafe Open-Ear Bluetooth Headphones redefine how you experience sound. Using innovative <strong>open-ear technology</strong>, these headphones rest gently above your ears, allowing ambient sounds like a passing car or a friendly greeting to filter through naturally while enveloping you in crisp, immersive audio. Whether you're navigating a bustling city street or enjoying a quiet evening at home, you’ll stay connected to your surroundings without sacrificing sound quality.\n        </p>\n        \n        <h3>Lightweight Design and Long-Lasting Battery</h3>\n        <p>\n            With a <strong>featherlight and ergonomic design</strong>, weighing just 28 grams, NG EarSafe headphones contour seamlessly to your ears, offering a barely-there feel that’s perfect for extended wear. Picture yourself powering through a marathon work session, embarking on a scenic commute, or pushing your limits at the gym. These headphones deliver all-day comfort without the pressure of traditional earbuds. Plus, their robust <strong>IPX5 water-resistant rating</strong> ensures they can withstand sweat or a sudden drizzle, making them a reliable companion for any adventure. With an impressive <strong>8-hour battery life</strong>, extendable to 24 hours with the sleek charging case, you’ll enjoy uninterrupted music, podcasts, or calls from dawn to dusk without scrambling for a charger.\n        </p>\n        \n        <h3>Advanced Connectivity and Clear Communication</h3>\n        <p>\n            Fueled by cutting-edge <strong>Bluetooth 5.0 technology</strong>, the NG EarSafe headphones provide a rock-solid wireless connection up to 33 feet, banishing frustrating dropouts and audio lag even in crowded environments. The integrated <strong>high-sensitivity microphone</strong>, enhanced with noise-canceling features, captures your voice with crystal-clear precision, transforming chaotic commutes into effortless hands-free conversations. Available in stylish shades like Midnight Black and Arctic White, these headphones don’t just perform. They make a statement. Whether you’re syncing to your favorite playlist, catching up with a friend, or unwinding with an audiobook, the NG EarSafe Open-Ear Bluetooth Headphones fuse safety, sophistication, and stellar sound into one game-changing package. Elevate your listening journey today!\n        </p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n    .footer-seo {color:#ddd;padding:30px;text-align:left;border-radius:8px}\n    .footer-seo h2 {color:#fff;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left}\n    .footer-seo h3 {color:#fff;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left}\n    .footer-seo p {font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}\n</style>",
